author: sync
title: طلاب الثانوية العامة بالبحيرة عن امتحاني التاريخ والفيزياء: الوقت غير كاف (فيديو)
text:
رصدت عدسة “فيتو” ردود أفعال طلاب الشهادة الثانوية العامة بمحافظة البحيرة ، وذلك عقب خروجهم من اللجان بعد انتهاء امتحاني مادتي الفيزياء والتاريخ حيث عبر الطلاب بآرائهم عن صعوبة الامتحانات واحتياجهم لزيادة الوقت المحدد للإجابة على أسئلة الإمتحانات.
استمرار رفع درجة الاستعداد القصوى بجميع الإدارات لامتحانات الثانوية وأكد إبراهيم الديب وكيل وزارة التربية والتعليم بالبحيرة ، أهمية الالتزام بتنفيذ كافة توجيهات محمد عبداللطيف وزير التربية والتعليم والتعليم الفني والدكتورة جاكلين عازر محافظ البحيرة، برفع درج الاستعداد والعمل على توفير الأجواء المناسبة أمام أبنائنا الطلاب لأداء امتحاناتهم بسهولة ويسر ودون أي معوقات.
الالتزام التام بالتعليمات الأمنية الخاصة بنقل صناديق الأسئلة وشدد على استمرار رفع درجة الاستعداد القصوى بجميع الإدارات التعليمية والالتزام بتنفيذ كافة القرارات والتعليمات الوزارية الخاصة بأعمال الامتحانات والتي تهدف إلى انتظام سير امتحان شهادة إتمام الدراسة الثانوية العامة للعام الدراسي ٢٠٢٤ / ٢٠٢٥ على الوجه الأكمل، وإنجاز الإجراءات المطلوبة، على نحو يحقق الأهداف المرجوة، وتحقيقا لصالح أبنائنا الطلاب مع الالتزام التام بالتعليمات الأمنية الخاصة بنقل صناديق الأسئلة والتنسيق الدائم مع الجهات الامنية لتأمين خطوط السير لضمان وصولها إلى اللجان فى الوقت المحدد.
تجهيز ١١٧ لجنة امتحانية على مستوى ١٧ إدارة تعليمية جدير بالذكر قد تم تجهيز ١١٧ لجنة امتحانية على مستوى ١٧ إدارة تعليمية بنطاق المحافظة بالبحيرة لاستقبال ٤٠٠٠٣ طالبًا وطالبة، منهم ٧٤٠١ طالب وطالبة بالشعبة الأدبية و٢٩٨٣١ طالب وطالبة بشعبة علمى علوم و٢٧٧١ طالبا وطالبة علمى رياضة بالإضافة إلى ٢٠١١ طالبا وطالبة بالنظام القديم (٢٣٩ طالبا وطالبة أدبى _ و١١٣ طالبا وطالبة علمى رياضة _ و١٦٥٩ علمى علوم)، كما تم تجهيز استراحات المراقبين والملاحظين (٤٠ استراحة) تم تزويدها بجميع المستلزمات التي تضمن راحتهم طوال فترة الامتحانات.
ونقدم لكم من خلال موقع ( فيتو )، تغطية ورصدًا مستمرًّا على مدار الـ 24 ساعة لـ أسعار الذهب ، أسعار اللحوم ، أسعار الدولار ، أسعار اليورو ، أسعار العملات ، أخبار الرياضة ، أخبار مصر ، أخبار اقتصاد ، أخبار المحافظات ، أخبار السياسة ، أخبار الحوداث ، ويقوم فريقنا بمتابعة حصرية لجميع الدوريات العالمية مثل الدوري الإنجليزي ، الدوري الإيطالي ، الدوري المصري ، دوري أبطال أوروبا ، دوري أبطال أفريقيا ، دوري أبطال آسيا ، والأحداث الهامة و السياسة الخارجية والداخلية بالإضافة للنقل الحصري لـ أخبار الفن والعديد من الأنشطة الثقافية والأدبية.

author: Matt Dolloff
title: Bruins collapse in third period, fall to Jets by 6-2 final
text:
The Boston Bruins lost their second straight game on Thursday night, by a 6-2 final to the Winnipeg Jets. Thursday marked the first time all season that the B’s allowed at least six goals in consecutive games, as goaltender Joonas Korpisalo stopped only 22-of-227 Jets shots (.815).
The Jets lifted off to an early 1-0 lead when Vladislav Namestnikov cleaned up a rebound with a backhand through Korpisalo during a power play. They momentarily thought they had a second goal minutes later, but the Bruins successfully challenged for offside to take it off the board.
Winnipeg took a 2-0 lead anyway later in the first period, when Mark Scheifele tipped in a long-distance shot by Neal Pionk. Bruins captain Brad Marchand cut the deficit in half late in the first, with a laser of a shot from the faceoff circle through Vezina favorite Connor Hellebuyck.
?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 31, 2025 After battling through a scoreless second period, the Bruins finally found the equalizer just 11 seconds into the third period – and during a penalty kill. The B’s generated an early shot on goal to force an offensive zone faceoff, then Elias Lindholm scored right off the draw to tie it 2-2.
Unfortunately, the tie was very short-lived, as the Jets answered just 24 seconds later with Scheifele’s second goal of the game to go back up at 3-2. Just 42 seconds after that, Nikolaj Ehlers scored by knocking the puck off the stick of Bruins defenseman Mason Lohrei and right into the Bruins net, marking a brutal blunder by the young blue liner.
Rhode Island native Parker Ford, playing in his first career NHL game, scored his first career goal later in the third to make it 5-2. Kyle Connor smacked home an empty-netter off a neutral-zone puck battle to make it 6-2, and that would be the final score.
The Columbus Blue Jackets have a chance to pass the Bruins in the second Eastern Conference wild card spot when they take on the Vegas Golden Knights out west on Thursday night.
Up Next: The Bruins will try to right the ship with another home game on Saturday, when they take on the New York Rangers at TD Garden.
Matt Dolloff is a writer and digital content producer for 98.5 The Sports Hub. Read all of his articles here .

author: 快科技
title: 31亿！我国大模型应用个人用户注册"爆表" 竟超全国人口规模2倍多|AI_新浪科技_新浪网
text:
快科技7月31日消息，近日，国家网信办披露，当前，AI 正以多元化的形式融入大众生活，通过网页、移动应用、API 接口、本地部署以及云服务部署等多种途径，全方位为用户提供服务。
据不完全统计，大模型应用领域呈现出爆发式增长。个人用户注册总数一路狂飙，已突破 31 亿大关；API 调用用户总数也相当可观，超过 1.59 亿。
或许有人会质疑，大模型注册人口数与我国实际人口总数并无直接可比性。但为了能更直观地感受这组数据的震撼力，我们不妨进行一番对比。
国家统计局相关页面显示，截至 2024 年末，我国总人口为 140828 万，约等于 14.0828 亿。
简单计算便可发现，31 亿是 14 亿的 2 倍多，这意味着大模型个人用户注册总数已经远远超越了全国人口规模。这说明平均每人注册大模型在 2 个以上
这一现象背后，反映出的是 AI 技术强大的吸引力和广阔的应用前景。
从日常的智能语音助手，到专业的行业数据分析模型，AI 正以润物细无声的方式改变着每个人的工作和生活方式。
而如此庞大的用户注册数量，也预示着 AI 市场蕴含着巨大的发展潜力，未来必将催生出更多的创新应用和商业模式。

author: redacao@odia.com.br (O Dia)
title: Kaká posa com todos os filhos no mesversário da caçula, Sarah: 'Minha pequena'
text: Kaká posa com os filhos, Luca, Isabella, Esther e Sarah no mesversário da caçulaReprodução/Instagram/Paula Zurc "11 meses da Sarah, sendo comemorados com antecedência. Inacreditável que a minha pequena já está prestes a fazer 1 ano!", escreveu a influenciadora na legenda da publicação. Nos cliques, o eterno craque posa ao lado da amada enquanto segura a primogênita do casal, Esther, que completou 3 anos no final do ano passado. Em outros registros, as meninas se reúnem com os filhos do primeiro casamento de Kaká: Luca, de 15 anos, e Isabella, de 12, para mostrar toda a beleza da família do ex-atacante. Também é possível notar a decoração da festa da postagem, que foi toda na temática da princesa Bela, do filme 'A Bela e A Fera'. Fãs correram para os comentários para admirar a semelhança entre o ex-camisa 10 e seus herdeiros, e aproveitaram para parabenizar a pequena Sarah: "As meninas estão fofas demais, mas é impossível não ver o sorriso do Luca idêntico ao do Kaká", admitiu uma internauta. "O Luca tá tão parecido com o Kaká", afirmou outro. "Felicidades à essa princesa linda, que Deus abençoe e proteja sempre", desejou uma terceira. "Se não tivessem com roupa diferente, dava pra confundir o Luca com o pai", contou mais uma.

When Aaron Rodgers recounted his very brief Game of Thrones cameo: "It was fun to be a part of it" Discuss Now Quarterback Aaron Rodgers made a cameo in "Game of Thrones." (Image source: Getty) Besides being a quarterback in the NFL, Aaron Rodgers has also tried his hand in an acting role. In July 2020, the quarterback, who played for the Green Bay Packers at the time, made an appearance on "10 Questions With Kyle Brandt" and was asked about his role on the hit series "Game of Thrones."
Rodgers told Brandt that he had a small role in the show's finale episode in May 2019. He went on to describe how small of a role it was and that it was a 'blink and miss it' type of moment.
"There's a scene where she (Arya) kind of comes down the steps and I'm there. And, then they flip it around and you can see me briefly again. So, it's one of those things just like right there, right there and that was it. But, it was fun to be a part of it," Rodgers told Brandt in July 2020. Trending •

Despite his small role, Rodgers told Brandt that he had much fun working on the set and appearing in the show.
Aaron Rodgers said nobody recognized him when he filmed "Game of Thrones" Aaron Rodgers is an avid fan of the series, and when he was offered the opportunity to make a cameo on the show in 2019, he didn't hesitate. In May 2019, he told Packers.com that when he arrived in Belfast, Ireland, to film his role, he wasn't recognized by anyone, which surprised him.
"In Belfast, they didn't care at all. They had no idea who I was. It was fun to be a part of it. I love the show. It's a fantastic show. A lot of great seasons," Rodgers told Packers.com. The former Green Bay Packers quarterback told the publication that it was a fun experience, especially since he loves watching the show. After his episode of "Game of Thrones" aired, the quarterback shared a look at his costume on Instagram.
"It was just for a few seconds, but I’ll always be thankful to have been on the penultimate episode of @gameofthrones #crazyepisodetonight," Rodgers wrote on Instagram in 2019. Aaron Rodgers also thanked everyone for the opportunity to be a part of the show, especially the final episode of the series, which was highly talked about by fans.
